    $f$ & $w$ & $f$ & $f$ & $w$ & $w$ & $f$ & $w$\\
    $f$ & $w$ & $w$ & $f$ & $w$ & $w$ & $f$ & $w$\\
    $w$ & $f$ & $f$ & $f$ & $f$ & $f$ & $w$ & $f$\\
    $w$ & $f$ & $w$ & $f$ & $w$ & $w$ & $f$ & $w$\\
    $w$ & $w$ & $f$ & $w$ & $w$ & $w$ & $f$ & $f$\\
    $w$ & $w$ & $w$ & $w$ & $w$ & $w$ & $f$ & $f$\\
