    \rightarrow (\forall x \alpha\rightarrow\beta)$
    \begin{align*}
      (1)\quad& \exists x \alpha \wedge \neg\beta &\text{Hypothese}\\
      (2)\quad& \underbrace{(\alpha \wedge \neg\beta)[x/c]}_{=\alpha
